  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

  <p>At Our AI Legacy, operated by Bezaleel Consulting Group ("we," "us," or "our"), we are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring the security of your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, store, and protect your information when you use our AI-powered video content generation platform.</p>

