  <p>When you connect your YouTube account, we collect and store:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Channel Information:</strong> Channel name, description, subscriber count, video count</li>
    <li><strong>Video Metadata:</strong> Video titles, descriptions, thumbnails, upload dates, duration</li>
    <li><strong>Playlist Data:</strong> Playlist names, video lists, organization structure</li>
    <li><strong>OAuth Tokens:</strong> Encrypted access and refresh tokens for ongoing YouTube access</li>
    <li><strong>Video Transcripts:</strong> Extracted from your YouTube videos for content generation</li>
  </ul>
  
  <div class="contact-info">
