    <li><strong>YouTube Integration:</strong> Import and organize your video content</li>
    <li><strong>AI Processing:</strong> Generate blogs, quizzes, discussion guides using Google Gemini and OpenAI</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>2.2 Platform Operations</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Authenticate users and maintain secure sessions</li>
    <li>Process payments and manage subscriptions</li>
    <li>Provide customer support and technical assistance</li>
